dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Alan Campbell. May I have your name, please?
Hello, Alan. My name is Tiffany Murphy.
Nice to meet you, Tiffany. Could you please provide me with your policy number for verification purposes?
Sure, it's one zero zero two five four.
Thank you, Tiffany. Can you also confirm your date of birth for security reasons?
Of course, it's the twenty-second of April, nineteen eighty-five.
Great, thank you for confirming that information. Is there anything specific you need assistance with today, Tiffany?
I wanted to check the status of a claim I filed last week.
I can assist with that. Let me pull up your file. Thank you for your patience, Tiffany.
Thank you for contacting us, Tiffany. Have a great day.
Thank you for contacting us, Tiffany. Have a great day.
